assignments.name: image_prompt
assignments.value: =A dynamic, visually captivating Digital Monster trading card featuring a vibrant fantasy creature with a dramatic, energized aesthetic. The card has a sleek rectangular design with glowing, stylized edges that reflect elemental attributes like fire, water, electricity, earth, or dark energy, based on '{{ $json.body.parameters.element }}'. The central creature '{{ $json.body.parameters.monster_name }}' is rendered prominently, posed in an action stance, surrounded by swirling elemental effects or ambient magic glow matching its type. The background showcases an immersive environment consistent with the monster's habitat: fiery volcanic landscapes, deep mystical forests, underwater realms, thunderous skies, or shadowy terrains. Text elements are clear, stylish, and subtly glowing:  Top-left: Monster Name '{{ $json.body.parameters.monster_name }}'  Top-right: Level '{{ $json.body.parameters.level }}' or rarity icon '{{ $json.body.parameters.rarity }}'  Bottom-left: Attack '{{ $json.body.parameters.attack_points }}' and Defense '{{ $json.body.parameters.defense_points }}' stats, stylized with elemental icons  Bottom-right: Special Ability '{{ $json.body.parameters.special_ability }}' prominently displayed with subtle illumination. Typography is modern and fantasy-inspired, clearly legible, and accented with gentle glows and shadows. Include customizable additional visual options: '{{ $json.body.parameters.visual_effect }}', and incorporate user-specific custom instructions: '{{ $json.body.parameters.custom_instructions }}'. The card should exude collectible, high-quality artwork vibes, suitable for popular digital monster trading games.
